message.body: Hey there. How's the weekend going for ya?
Hey. Not that much happening this far, been relaxing and catching up on stuff.
That's good. Ready for your weekend shifts?
Not going in tonight, only tomorrow.
Gotcha. I'm so bored right now. Finished my assignments around 3 but don't want to start anything until Monday. Help meee
Leave.
You're done!
Lol I wish. My manager has been wanting us to do work to produce a running log to justify expanding our team in anticipation of the introduction of new products
Can't show that we're being unproductive. Any plans with your Friday night?
Not really. Going out with my sister to do an errand and then that's pretty much it.
I started watching season 4 history and lore of GoT
And???
Nice touch how they have similar voice actors if not the same.
Yup.
I'm only half way in. I stopped to get dinner with Thuy and Cindy last night
Cool.
I like it so far. Though I'm more inclined to get a recap watching before Sunday night
How are you going to recap?
Either speed binge watch or find a credible recap video
Unless you have suggestions
Aren't you going to DC?
How are you going to have time to binge?

I have no idea. Here's the rundown: Saturday morning- get mouths and drive to dc, morning parade, afternoon blossoms, early dinner, drive home that night? Sunday- food festival at Manayunk (I'd like to invite you to this if you're available) go home to rest and find recap video, watch GoT with Cindy and whoever else will be around pending Cindy is still hosting
Sure, I'll go to the festival if my schedule is good. I'll let you know. I would fibre cap, or watch the last episode of last season.
*find a recap
Watching the whole season may be too ambitious.
But hey, if you're really determined, go for it.
Haha. It might be considering I'll be out and about. I don't know if I can watch snow watch ygritte die again.
John snow. Yuh noe nuthin. /gah
When you're done with your sister you wanna grab a bite at zento? They have this amazing scallop dish they're running as a special. If it does well enough they might put it on the menu
When are you planning to go?
Come now lol
I was running an errand not far from here so I'm already sitting
You're there already?
Gotcha.
Well if you're already eating I'm probably not going to make it soon enough.
That's alright. I'll catch ya when I get back from D.C. then
Still leaving tonight right?
That's the plan. No set time. Unless you want to get tea or something
I kind of want Bambu...
I could do that.
You don't have to. Don't you have to pack?
It's a day trip. I just need my tooth brush and a change of underwear lol
If you're leaving tonight, don't you need pajamas and other clothes?
All in the bag. I'm pro at this lol
Okay then, I could be there in 15.
Cool?
If you don't mind waiting a little. I have to close out my check
Okay, I have to get back soon by 9 though...
*back home
Ok. Get going and I'll be in my way
Okay.
I am here
￼Cheese lol
Awww, there goes the siblings.
My friends are DRUNK right now.
Haha. Are you doing ok?
I know it isn't as fun being the only sober one
I'm okay, just not in the bar/dancing mood right now.
The music isn't bad.
I don't mind being sober. Just not feeling it tonight.
Yeah. At least you got to see your peeps
￼The siblings and myself were having a good laugh at how ridiculous this concept is. Why yes, I would love savory peeps. Katherine initially thought I made it up that savory was on there
Ohhh those are risky peeps.
I'm about to pass out. I hope you get home safe whenever you decide to finish. Goodnight Phuong!
Night!
